  documentBody: 'Employee IDs keep disappearing, but nobody is ever told they were
    fired. Their desks are cleaned before anyone gets to work. I asked HR.


    They
    told me the records had "always looked like this."

    I know they didn''t.


    If
    you''re reading this, keep looking.

    Someone archived everything instead
    of deleting it'
